<ext_description linkend="Condition_evaluation_arm">The condition evaluation ARM provides the construct to record evaluation results of criteria parameters and condition summary. It also provides a reference to the object for which the condition is evaluated. 
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Condition_evaluation_arm  Entity: Condition_evaluation  
   <express_ref linkend="condition_evaluation:arm:Condition_evaluation_arm.Condition_evaluation"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Condition_evaluation_arm.Condition_assertion">
        The recording of result in evaluating a condition. The conclusion of asserting a condition is based on the result of the relevant criterion.
      </ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Condition_evaluation_arm  Entity: Condition_evaluation  Attribute: assertion 
   <express_ref linkend="condition_evaluation:arm:Condition_evaluation_arm.Condition_evaluation.assertion"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Condition_evaluation_arm.Condition_assertion.assertion">
          the result of evaluation.
        </ext_description>
